commit eec83a184b28a99a880e89dd2c0307ca3dad8d33
Author: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Oct 22 15:49:10 2025 +0300

    Fixed an issue that led to deletion of persisted table stats
    
    The `update()` call with empty stats led to deleting all stats,
    since the method first deletes all existing table and col stats
    before starting to rewrite them to disk.
    
    Follows: #18244
    (cherry picked from commit 114e47c51d454af27064a2e9b2af0bb94f590026)

